### =============================================================================
### Fleet Service — http://localhost:3003
### =============================================================================
### Usage: Open in JetBrains IDE or VS Code (REST Client extension)
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Health
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Create vehicle
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create a vehicle (valid)
# @name createVehicle
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "AB-123-CD",
  "brand": "Mercedes-Benz",
  "model": "Classe E",
  "year": 2022
}

### Create another vehicle
# @name createVehicle2
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "EF-456-GH",
  "brand": "BMW",
  "model": "Série 5",
  "year": 2023
}

### Create vehicle — duplicate number plate (expect 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "AB-123-CD",
  "brand": "Peugeot",
  "model": "508",
  "year": 2021
}

### Create vehicle — missing brand (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "IJ-789-KL",
  "brand": "",
  "model": "308",
  "year": 2022
}

### Create vehicle — year too old (expect 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "MN-000-OP",
  "brand": "Renault",
  "model": "Laguna",
  "year": 2010
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Get vehicle
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get vehicle by ID — replace with ID from createVehicle response
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID

### Get vehicle — not found (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000000

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### List active vehicles
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List all active vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Update vehicle
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Update model only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "Classe E 300"
}

### Update multiple fields
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Mercedes-Benz",
  "model": "Classe E 400",
  "year": 2023
}

### Update number plate — duplicate (expect 409)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number_plate": "EF-456-GH"
}

### Update year — invalid (expect 422)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": 2005
}

### Update — vehicle not found (expect 404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Toyota"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Activate / Deactivate
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Deactivate vehicle
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID/deactivate

### List active vehicles — deactivated vehicle should not appear
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles

### Activate vehicle
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/REPLACE_WITH_VEHICLE_ID/activate

### List active vehicles — vehicle should reappear
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicles

### Deactivate — vehicle not found (expect 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicles/00000000-0000-7000-8000-000000000000/deactivate